{"id": "1191658933404831797", "channel_id": "1191658933404831797", "type": 0, "author_id": "1190644849687408800", "author_name": "guyi0176", "author_bot": false, "content": "游戏内语言可以设置成简/繁中\n但是公告只能看繁中（虽说也能看懂但费劲）（市面上也有免费好用的简繁转换软件）\n好奇下有设置简中公告，或者公告语言同步设置的想法/计划吗（）", "timestamp": "2024-01-02T08:27:09.676000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1191658934038179870", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-02-16-23-22-66_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 148331, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1191658933404831797/1191658934038179870/Screenshot_2024-01-02-16-23-22-66_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=6a00415d&is=69feefdd&hm=dd850e365ea3c46d1053527c33b7ee253c891faa224d30f94110f6e826d986c5&"}, {"id": "1191658934432452659", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-02-16-23-41-47_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 63501, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1191658933404831797/1191658934432452659/Screenshot_2024-01-02-16-23-41-47_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=6a00415d&is=69feefdd&hm=ddb2c6c1e73167987dfc8e93e9c25fbb88e406594ee9ff1843e4ad094956b232&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1191658933404831797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」公告可以也设置成简中吗", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
